title: Panzer III: Medium Tank (2005)
description:
Panzer III: Medium Tank (2005) 

Meet the Panzer III medium tank, one of Germany&#039;s showpiece weapons in World War II, often appearing in newsreel footage documenting early Nazi victories in Europe. Though it could easily hold its own against the Allied forces&#039; tanks, the Panzer III met its match on the Eastern Front against the Russian T-34. By the end of the war, it had been shifted to secondary fronts and was often used as a command tank rather than on the main battlefield.
